We don't actually need to spawn a boss enemy. 
We simply spawn the chest on the last enemy killed, but we can still have a "Final Spawn Action"

Spawn Wave:

- Number of enemies.
- Enemy Stat Modifiers.
- Wave time limit.

Spawn Action:

- Type of enemy to spawn.
- Number of enemies to spawn in the action.
- Spawn Pattern.

Enemy Definition:

- Enemy Prefab.
- Enemy Base Stats.

Enemy:

- Enemy Scope
- Enemy Stats
- Enemy Health Handler
- Enemy Movement Handler
~ Enemy Attack Handler
~ Enemy Ability Handler